title: Proposal to allow modification of sale price without having to cancel and create a new listing.
body: We've all done it, misread the market (too low or too high) and had the urge to modify the sales price.   I have dreams of a simple "edit listing" button that actually let you modify price.  The button exists....but i can't change my santa hat from 998 GHST to 1300 GHST without cumbersome steps.
choices: Yes! Why isn't this a thing?
author: 0xd32f222283D295f93664B11faAC967e6826b635f
